"{\"uid\": \"usmagazine.com-stylish-news-ariana-grande-cynthia-erivo-wickedly-stun-at-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Ariana GrandeandCynthia Erivo's arrival at the2024 Summer Olympicsis wicked good.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 81, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday, July 26, theWickedcostars coordinated in different '50s-esque evening gowns as they stepped out to help celebrate the Opening Ceremony of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 83, \"to\": 248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Grande, 31, looked angelic while channeling her onscreen character Glinda the Good Witch in a baby pink midi dress by Thom Browne.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Glinda\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For some extra sparkle and shine, fashion stylistMimi Cuttrelladded Swarovski jewelry pieces to the actress' look as she posed in front of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Erivo, 37, she paid tribute to herWickedcharacter, Elphaba, by choosing emerald green for her ensemble.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elphaba\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The actress stunned in a custom Louis Vuitton strapless gown styled byJason Bolden.\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0106142344104546e-30, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She completed her look with a wide-brim hat, Roberto Coin jewelry\\u00a0and nails perfected by artistRose Hackle.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hackle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hackle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hackle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hackle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just hours before reuniting with Grande, Erivo appeared on theTodayshow and gushed about the unbreakable bond she shares with her costar.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by TODAY (@todayshow)    \\\"She just is one of the sweetest, kindest people I have ever met,\\\" she toldHoda KotbandSavannah Guthrie.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woody_Guthrie\", \"score\": 0.9999999727263006, \"rank\": 2.7273755647298943e-08, \"text\": \"Guthrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woody_Guthrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woody_Guthrie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have just had such a wonderful time doing this together and we have had such an experience learning about each other, learning about what we need and supporting one another.\\\"\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For her morning show appearance, Erivo completely transformed her look into what she described as \\\"teacher's pet\\\" vibes.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She accessorized her plaid set with a pink ring that was a symbol of \\\"my Glinda\\\" Grande.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1502